    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/a5f525e15297de509d1427329b459db7.poster.avif?t=1764368948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/a5f525e15297de509d1427329b459db7.webm?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/a5f525e15297de509d1427329b459db7.mp4?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chaos is breaking through the cracks of a fractured world, and only the warriors chosen by the Archetypes can stop its return. <br> <br><strong>Trinity Archetype</strong> is a Skill-Crafting Roguelike RPG that blends deckbuilder-style progression with strategic, turn-based JRPG combat. Fight, level up, learn new skills, and customize them with hundreds of Runes to create unique builds and broken synergies that make every run feel different. The possibilities are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/f4df5ac9b9a3dce85af712498dc7cbf8.avif?t=1764368948\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/b1c1643665aacfb968cd6886ef71f836.poster.avif?t=1764368948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/b1c1643665aacfb968cd6886ef71f836.webm?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/b1c1643665aacfb968cd6886ef71f836.mp4?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your party and unlock new skills after each battle, then enhance them with <strong>Runes</strong> to add powerful effects and discover devastating synergies. There are countless combinations to explore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/0d5c18d8b979f7dd66c08df25402e945.avif?t=1764368948\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/ec823f651c21c175f072df893996e1c2.poster.avif?t=1764368948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/ec823f651c21c175f072df893996e1c2.webm?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/ec823f651c21c175f072df893996e1c2.mp4?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a leader to <strong>Inspire</strong> your allies and trigger powerful party-wide effects, then <strong>Boost</strong> your skills to deliver even stronger damage and bonus effects. Chaining inspires and boosted skills together lets you unleash broken combos that can wipe out enemies in a single turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/e83e2ceca2c9bed26882035c63cb32dc.avif?t=1764368948\" width=800 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/4fb30448fa7e21914651f482a7637be0.poster.avif?t=1764368948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/4fb30448fa7e21914651f482a7637be0.webm?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/4fb30448fa7e21914651f482a7637be0.mp4?t=1764368948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>hundreds of Runes</strong>, dozens of skills, multiple playable characters, artifacts, items, events, and enemies, no two runs will ever feel the same. Unlock more options as you play and experiment with new builds each time you challenge Chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763580/extras/3cfb991af249630d9a950b65dc823f38.avif?t=1764368948\" width=1200 height=160 /></span></p>",
